OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FIt won't be a washout this Easter
OL,7,Fweekend, but strong and potentially
OL,8,Fdisruptive winds are set to sweep
OL,9,Facross parts of the UK, with the worst
OL,10,Fconditions expected from Saturday into
OL,11,FEaster Sunday.
OL,13,FForecasters say the changing weather
OL,14,Fpattern will bring a mix of sunshine,
OL,15,Fshowers and strengthening winds - with
OL,16,Fwarnings already in place for some
OL,17,Fareas.
OL,19,FCalm conditions before a change
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
