PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FIn the lead-up to the weekend,
OL,7,Fconditions remain relatively settled
OL,8,Ffor many.
OL,10,FA ridge of high pressure is still
OL,11,Fholding on across England and Wales,
OL,12,Fbringing largely dry but often cloudy
OL,13,Fskies.
OL,15,FFurther north, a weakening cold front
OL,16,Fwill gradually sink southwards,
OL,17,Fintroducing a fresher feel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
