PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,Fy Friday night, a brief ridge allows
OL,7,Fcolder air to move in, leading to a
OL,8,Fchilly start on Saturday, with a touch
OL,9,Fof frost possible in places but this
OL,10,Fquieter spell will be short-lived.
OL,12,FStrong winds set to develop
OL,14,FA more significant change arrives as a
OL,15,Fsurge of cold air dives south from
OL,16,FCanada into the North Atlantic,
OL,17,Fstrengthening the jet stream and
OL,18,Fhelping to spin up a deep area of low
OL,19,Fpressure to the northwest of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
