PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FMet Office Deputy Chief Meteorologist
OL,7,FDan Holley says this will bring a
OL,8,Fspell of very strong winds later on
OL,9,FSaturday, continuing overnight into
OL,10,FEaster Sunday morning.
OL,12,FYellow weather warnings have been
OL,13,Fissued for Scotland, Northern Ireland,
OL,14,Fand northern parts of England and
OL,15,FWales.
OL,17,FWhere winds will be strongest
OL,19,FGusts are expected to reach 50 to
OL,20,F60mph quite widely, with 60 to 70mph
OL,21,Fpossible in exposed locations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
