OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FIn parts of western and northern
OL,7,FScotland, particularly across coasts
OL,8,Fand hills, there is a chance of 80 to
OL,9,F90mph gusts.
OL,11,FWhile there will be some rain at
OL,12,Ftimes, it is the strength of the wind
OL,13,Fthat is likely to have the greatest
OL,14,Fimpact, with the potential for travel
OL,15,Fdisruption and difficult conditions
OL,16,Foutdoors.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
