OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FImproving into Easter Sunday and Monday
OL,8,FThe strongest winds are expected to
OL,9,Fease through Easter Sunday as the low
OL,10,Fpressure system clears into the North
OL,11,FSea.
OL,13,FBrighter conditions will follow, with
OL,14,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,15,Falthough it will remain breezy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
