PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775070658
OL,3,CEaster weather: Strong wind warnings
OL,4,Cissued with gusts up to 90mph possible
OL,6,FBy Easter Monday, many areas will see
OL,7,Fa further improvement, with lighter
OL,8,Fwinds and a fair amount of dry
OL,9,Fweather. However, cloud and rain may
OL,10,Fbegin to edge into western parts later
OL,11,Fin the day.
OL,13,FThe bigger picture
OL,15,FOverall, the Easter weekend will bring
OL,16,Fchangeable spring weather ` not a
OL,17,Fcomplete washout, but unsettled at
OL,18,Ftimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
